data.text: @SalgadoPhoto_ March 6, 2020: Baseball Tourney in the DFW area with Socorro Baseball.  These would be the last games.  Traveled to Lubbock on March 10, 2020 only to be recalled because of COVID.  #Senior https://t.co/1UOEYj8rHX
@SalgadoPhoto_ Watching and writing about @Ricardo_Pepi9’s debut for FC Dallas. Feels like a lifetime ago. https://t.co/9He4YCvd24
@SalgadoPhoto_ I was at that concert with my Dad, crazy to think a few weeks later everything changed
@dani_phantom10 I miss the fun parts of journalism 🥲 https://t.co/1FHFaCPVVB

@SalgadoPhoto_ Getting ready to move out of my apartment and into my favorite house. Also, we were about to travel to Dallas for a concert, which was supposed to be the first event held at the Rangers new ballpark ☹️

@SalgadoPhoto_ I had an interview planned with them. I was going to surprise my dad and take him with me to shoot it so he could finally meet one of his favorite people, @genesimmons. All meet and greets/ interviews were cancelled that week. 🥲
@ebau27 Oh no! I hope you got to celebrate to some degree!
